title: Haha! Diqiu Renn
synopsis: The story of this season inherits the plot of the first season, haha ​​and ha Xiaolong once again stay on the earth. Help Lanlan fulfill his dream of universe exploration last season. At the same time, Proxima Star encounters a new crisis. The artificial intelligence system is destroyed by the impact of the solar molecular storm. The highly developed Proxima Beta is paralyzed because of the loss of its initial production capacity. If you want to help Proximity return to its original state, you can only rely on Haha to continue exploring on the earth step by step, collecting various energy to help Proximity rebuild. 　　On the earth, haha ​​explored the professions of pottery, costume designer, gardener, etc., and also learned about the professional skills and professional knowledge needed by the people of the earth from multiple angles such as physics, chemistry, biology, literature, and fine arts. Ha Xiaolong, who has always wanted to reproduce the age of the dinosaurs on the earth, tried his best to make trouble and made a lot of jokes for Haha and Lanlan. Lan Lan and her friends also discovered that the normal operation of the world is inseparable from the hard work and dedication of all walks of life. Every profession has its existence value and social responsibilities. Only by doing every job well can society develop steadily and human history can develop in an orderly manner. For the two aliens, Haha was anxious to repair the spacecraft and return to space; Gongsunlan also wanted to help Haha repair the spacecraft for a dazzling space journey; will the cute pet Ha Xiaolong remember him What about the ambition to destroy the peace of the universe? And their most dangerous enemy is Gongsun Lan's adversary, Sima Qingkong, who is the leader of the "From the Future" space science interest group. When the spacecraft was repaired and haha ​​was about to return to their own planet, Gongsun Lan and his friends realized that what Haha brought to them was not just alien technology, the universe’s knowledge, but also a brand new career. Cognitive and knowledge mastery. The reconstruction of Proxima Centauri has also been completed, and haha ​​has to face the historic choice of going back or staying. Can Lan Lan's dream of flying in the universe be realized? Can Ha Xiaolong succeed in his ambition to restore the dinosaur empire? Haha, whether to stay on Earth or return to the universe, return to Proxima to continue his interstellar mission, these contents will be answered in this season. (translated from douban)

title: Orient
synopsis: Five years ago, Musashi made a promise with his friend Kojirou Kanemaki that once they grew up, they would become samurai, form a league, and go on demon-slaying quests. But since then, things have changed. With demons now being praised and worshipped by society, the samurai are shunned and disgraced. Afraid of revealing his dream of becoming a samurai, Musashi blends into the town's dogma by becoming a miner while secretly polishing his swordsmanship. Meanwhile, despite being a direct descendant of a samurai, Kojirou gives up on his promise to his old friend. However, after saving Musashi from a near-death experience, his perspective shifts. Although still conflicted, Kojirou embarks on a journey with Musashi in the hopes of figuring out his true feelings. Fighting against all odds, the duo dives headfirst into the unknown world of beast-slaying, not knowing what life has in store for them. Now astride iron horses, the fifteen-year-old heroes plan to restore the tarnished reputation of the samurai and purge the world of demons.
